With regards to switching from estimating multi-sig to single-sig -- 

Currently, the price lookup endpoint tries to figure out how many UTXOs will fund the transactions (via the core wallet address) -- obviously, right now, that estimation is wrong because the funding addresses will be different. So instead, I'll use a dummy single-sing address / pk rather than forcing the client to pass that information --- to get single_sig, pass the query string `single_sig=1`

```
